embeds.description:
**Issues with your setup -**
You can easily spot issues in your setup by running `/ess version`. Make sure you are not running mismatched versions of your Core jar, and any addons you use. 

Make sure you have:
- [EssentialsX Chat](https://essentialsx.net/downloads.html)
- [Vault](https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/34315/)
- A Supported [Permission Plugin](https://luckperms.net/download)

**Issues with LuckPerms -**
If the Prefix or Suffix is not displayed correctly by running `/lp user <user> info`, it hasn't been properly set in LuckPerms. 

`/lp user <user> meta info` will give you more information on any prefixes/suffixes you may have. For further LuckPerms support, you may go to the [LuckPerms Discord](https://discord.gg/LuckPerms).
